# Content Controller Endpoints
# Base URL: http://localhost:3001
# Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

### Create training content (protected)
POST http://localhost:3001/training-content/contents
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}

{
  "title": "Introduction to NestJS",
  "type": "VIDEO",
  "url": "https://example.com/video.mp4",
  "moduleId": "<module-id>"
}

### Get contents by module ID (protected)
GET http://localhost:3001/training-content/contents/{{moduleId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{TOKEN}}
